    <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
    <p>Solid Properties shall not be liable for any indirect or consequential damages arising from your use of this website or our services.</p>

    <h2>Governing Law</h2>
    <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of California.</p>

    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-10">Last updated: May 2025</p>
